txt.en: 'There are many things that must be done to prepare a wooden structure and turn it into something that could be a home one day. Beds, tables, chairs, dressers, lanterns, flowers, plateware, all of the things that one needs to live a happy and fulfilling life will need to be brought in and added before we can expect someone to be ready to move in.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
House of the Norcrofts: Enhancements III
